<h2>Introduction</h2>

This is an activity based on the game Dreidel, a typical game played by Jews during Chanukah. Students will complete the below objectives through two activities (recommended over two sessions) in which they complete the dreidel craft and communicate how to do make it. 

Objectives: Students will be better able to...
<ul>
<li> Realize instructions from a video into a 3D object
<li> Communicate a process in a short video 
<li> Respectfully show curiosity towards other cultures 
</li>
</ul>



