<h3>Step 5: Let's Play</h3>

Now, you can go ahead and play dreidel with your partners! Here is a how-to video on how to play.

<div class="youtube">
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A0WGb5Pnmfc" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div>


The basics are, spin and do an action. The actions are: 
* _shin:_ put a piece in
* _gimel:_ you get everything in the pot
* _hey:_ you get half of the pot
* _nun:_ nothing happens




